text: Abdukareem Adebisi Bamdele "Bisi" Akande (born 16 January 1939) is a Nigerian politician of Yoruba heritage. He was the Governor of Osun State from the year 1999 to 2003. == References == Category:1939 births Category:Nigerian politicians Category:Living people Category:People from Osun State
title: Adebisi Akande
